        <item>
            <title>1.4.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 13:43:42 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>8</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- **Automatic extension updater** — Canopy now detects when the Claude CLI version is newer than the installed extension and offers a one-click update directly from the VS Marketplace. No VSCode required.
- Extensions are installed to `~/Library/Application Support/Canopy/extensions/`, keeping `~/.vscode/` untouched
- Update progress shown in launcher with download/install states and retry on failure

### Changes
- Extension discovery now checks Canopy's own directory first, then falls back to `~/.vscode/extensions/`
- Version comparison uses numeric ordering (fixes `2.1.9` vs `2.1.10` sorting)
- Old extension versions in Canopy's directory are automatically cleaned up after updates
]]></description>
